title: Moe Learned A Painful Lesson Last Week
description:
Moe accidentally cut himself after a glass broke in his kitchen. At first, he thought nothing of the cut, but days later, he was still in pain. Why? Because clearly there was glass in his foot! How'd he get it out? He tells us...
